<HEADLINE> Major Chinese TV Picture Tube Bulb Project </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZHENGZHOU, March 8 (Xinhua) -- The third phase of a color TV
picture tube bulb manufacturing company in the city of Anyang in
central China's Henan Province went into operation today.
</P>
<P>
The 625-million-yuan project will enable the Anyang Color
Picture Tube Bulb Company to produce 2.5 million 29-inch bulbs
annually, with five production lines.
</P>
<P>
The move is meant to meet the growing demand for color TVs, as
7 new production lines to manufacture 29-inch tubes are being
installed in the country.
</P>
