and rural enterprises, Zhu said this is a kind of corruption.
Though the central authorities have repeatedly reiterated that
farmers' burden should be alleviated, the related policies have
not been implemented in many areas, he added.
</P>
<P>
Energetic efforts will be made in this regard, Zhu said.
