<HEADLINE> Romania, Netherlands Sign Agreements on Cooperation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, March 7 (Xinhua) -- Romania and the Netherlands have
signed a series of agreements on avoidance of double taxation,
inter-governmental cooperation, and cooperation in fighting
corruption and organized crime.
