<HEADLINE> Colombian Coffee Prices Drop </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SANTAFE DE BOGOTA, March 7 (Xinhua) -- Colombian coffee price
has dropped from 366,875 pesos to 317,750 pesos a bag.
</P>
