<P>
WASHINGTON, March 7 (Xinhua) -- Former world No. 1 Steffi Graf
of Germany beat Thailand's Tamarine Tanasugarn 6-4, 6-0 in the
second round of the Evert Cup tennis tournament in Indian Wells on
Saturday.
